{"tid":1589400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個忠實的吉野家支持者，我有野想同你壓連登仔講","createTime":"2019-09-23T09:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:42:14.000Z","uid":245201,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9aacf1998a5d97c22296512bce6b97e0d37ec3e1","tid":1589400,"uid":245201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"吓，冇人嘅喂？<br />\n連登仔聲勢浩大講就係威係勢，點知上到黎食個下午茶全場4個都唔知有冇（計埋我在内）<br />\n唔撚係掛，身為藍絲嘅我都忍唔住要串吓你地了。<br />\n好喇，知你地都係得個講字，乜柒含動力都冇。<br />\n總結食評：份量唔算多，對連登仔黎講15<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpcUDLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpcUDLe.jpg&h=b6cb970a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蚊抵到爛啦，牛肉飯同吉野家差唔多味，汁偏淡，性價比高。<br />\n<br />\n唯獨是成個場静英英，唔講仲以為清明。"},{"pid":"a6c297db74bbef64cb09b7c44d0b1f5448431a1c","tid":1589400,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"星期幾呀?仲要慈雲山 下午茶時段無咩人都正常啦"},{"pid":"6dd05f4db8537dcad26c036ca605c3aa0eae5d73","tid":1589400,"uid":40828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"頭先啱啱先去完深水埗嗰間，全場滿座喎"},{"pid":"d7b729d7fd3d75375ea539765bd4a0460de23c71","tid":1589400,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:57:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>十一國殤 全民黑衣</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ishNdyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FishNdyx.jpg&h=21d2a745&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTDkyyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTDkyyx.jpg&h=565c80c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26e2c06977427b34fc28543ddf3fbb59ae671482","tid":1589400,"uid":245201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd05f4db8537dcad26c036ca605c3aa0eae5d73","tid":1589400,"uid":40828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:48:4